title: Bon Iver at the Rock and Roll Hotel 02-18-2008 (individual mp3s)
description:
I did not record this show, but I was in attendance (my 2nd of 3 Bon Iver shows in 8 months in the DC area). The audio comes from NPR, while the full torrent was uploaded by samuelbeckett22. I simply split the songs into separate mp3 files. This show was the night of the official release of "For Emma, Forever Ago" which everyone in the audience had obviously already been listening to for months.

Set List:
npr intro
flume
lump sum
skinny love
the wolves (act I and II)
blindsided 
creature fear
for emma
